GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 7th February, 2006
18 Magha, 1927 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 7th February,
2006, Dr. Dasari Narayana Rao relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of State in the Ministry of Mines. He will continue to hold the charge of the
office of Minister of State in the Ministry of Coal.
(K.L. Sharma)
